{"tid":1647883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］大佬個成半個熱門都係侵","createTime":"2019-10-12T02:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T03:47:35.000Z","uid":74622,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2465165d2ddce7f7a96bede07066c579e82cd1","tid":1647883,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:54:54.000Z","msg":"侵係講咗啲嘢<br />\n但有邊次係跟返句說話去做<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得美國係民主自由國家<br />\n<br />\n共雪 South Park Zedd讚South Park post<br />\nNBA 國會 人權法etc.<br />\n<br />\n邊撚個話外國戰線已完？<br />\n佢哋唔係奉旨出聲<br />\n係佢哋都覺得佢哋嘅人權自由被侵犯<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅事已經connect 咗唔少人<br />\n<br />\n如果侵真係跟佢嘅說話去做<br />\n一意孤行 唔聽市民嘅聲音 同中共極權冇撚分別<br />\n由得香港嘅 嚟緊連唔連到任都成問題<br />\n<br />\n唔該係哋咪撚再屌侵侵<br />\nBe Humble."},{"pid":"633e726ed170b4fb7ba6bb3f8f065c0506e20da4","tid":1647883,"uid":317257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:55:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e67fcdaff104ca1dbb31db5b105b29deed5cb7d3","tid":1647883,"uid":1212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"[文宣工作] 你今日air 左未 ? 原來大家忘記左ad<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n阻阻大家"},{"pid":"d6ca87b9ccd729383594c044626ee607179b8e24","tid":1647883,"uid":303124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:56:06.000Z","msg":"場運動因為你地亂搞活動就黎要輸喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1647794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1647794</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5b190948fb64b8422451d97d26f91a0a6472fb1","tid":1647883,"uid":74622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:56:22.000Z","msg":"You"},{"pid":"2f63c055410f449205cef6eb55c85e622666a36a","tid":1647883,"uid":171192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T02:57:06.000Z","msg":"見到有人利用侵番話吹風話唔好理美國戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n